log<trace<debug<info<warn<error<fatal<off

selenium grid
------------------

standalonego to cmd and type
java -jar selenium-grid-server.jar standalone
and it will give you a link  http://172.31.224.1:4444, open it in browser

hub

docker images needed 
-----------------------
1 hub
2 linux - firefox
3 linux - chrome

for hub - docker pull selenium/hub
for linufirefox- docker pull selenium/node-firefox
for linux chrome - docker pull selenium/node-chrome
all container should be part of a single network


-------run docker yaml file in the project to setup grid-------------
go to the location of file , take cmd and run command
docker-compose up


